Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.08,0:22:03.54,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs49.5\bord3.375}kimochi wo tsutaeru no
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.54,0:22:06.59,NozakiED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}nhưng thật khó nói ra
